#. module: it_hardware
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:it_hardware.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Company is a specialized IT Sales Establishment that focuses on providing a diverse selection of IT components for sale. The product contains laptops, RAM, accessories, CCTV cameras, and other related items. In addition to product\n"
"            sales, it is also offering installation and repair services for these components."
